original_title: Dash Berlin - Live @ Ultra Music Festival Miami Mainstage 2015
overview: Ultra Music Festival 2015. In the middle of the pouring rain. Dash Berlin wrote history surprising the crowd with one of the most emotional, powerful and energetic sets the festival has ever seen and proved to be right at home at the big main stage.
tagline: Miami. Ultra Music Festival 2015. In the middle of the pouring rain. Dash Berlin.
title: Dash Berlin - Live at Ultra Music Festival Miami Mainstage 2015
